question: How many people lived in Odense Municipality, Denmark on July 1, 2022?
asked_question_translated: Koliko ljudi je 1. julija 2022 živelo v občini Odense na Danskem?
answer: Po podatkih, na dan 1. julija 2022, je v občini Odense na Danskem živelo približno 206.305 ljudi.
answer_translated_eng: According to the data, on 1 July 2022, there were approximately 206,305 people living in Odense municipality, Denmark.
